  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: Only iOS. See righ side of the blue background for Syncing:\r\n![46714](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/6584810/31828168-d30b01cc-b5b9-11e7-9f1a-8bf08ce38fcb.jpg)\r\n\r\nSame for Error loading data message:\r\n\r\n![63757](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/6584810/31829684-575a835e-b5be-11e7-9926-fbe8b61b9c8d.jpg)\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nas in design https://github.com/status-im/status-react/issues/2144\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- to get Syncing warning: Switch to Network Ropsten or Rinkeby to get syncing started\r\n- open Wallet\r\n- to get Error loading data: switch off network for device, open wallet, pull down\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: release 0.9.12\r\n* Operating System: \r\nReal device iPhone 7 plus, iOs 11.0.3\r\n",
